condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :PA Section I, A.4 | Description :XETDZ MC shall furnish to the Bank, for approval, a prospective annual work andbudget plan for the Project by December 15 of each year of Project implementation, commencing on December 15, 2014, includingdetails on the planned program of activities, procurementplan and budget for the following calendar year in form and substance asset forth in the Operational Manual. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section I, A.4 | Description :XETDZ MC shall, by September 15, 2013, furnish to the Bank, for approval, aninitial work and budget plan covering the first seventeen months of Project Implementation, including details on the plannedprogram of activities, procurement plan and budget for such prospective period in form and substance as set forth in theOperational Manual. | Due Date :15-Sep-2013

Finance Agreement :PA Section II, A.1 | Description :XETDZ MC shall monitor and evaluate the progress of the Project and prepareProject Reports on the basis of indicators agreed with the Bank and set forth in the Operational Manual. Each such Project Reportshall cover the period of one calendar semester, and shall be furnished to the Borrower and to the Bank not later than 45 daysafter the end of the period covered by such report. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section II, B.2 | Description :XETDZ MC shall prepare and furnish to the Bank, as part of the Project Report,interim unaudited financial reports for the Project covering the semester, in form and substance satisfactory to the Bank. |Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section II, B.3 | Description :XETDZ MC shall have its financial statements referred to above audited byindependent auditors acceptable to the Bank annually. XETDZ MC shall ensure that the audited financial statements for each periodshall be (a) furnished to the Borrower and the Bank not later than six months after the end of the period; and (b) made publiclyavailable in a timely fashion and in a manner. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, A.1 | Description :XETDZ MC shall have entered into a contract for the construction and at least5 years of operation and maintenance of the wastewater treatment plant of the Project, with an entity or entities duly qualified toperform such tasks, all under terms and conditions acceptable to the Bank. | Due Date :30-Jun-2014

Finance Agreement :PA Section IV, A.2 | Description :For each of the Borrower’s fiscal years starting 2018, the WastewaterTreatment Plant, should have total revenues equivalent to notless than its total operating expenses, excluding depreciation. |Frequency :Yearly
